lines.text: What a bitch. I hope she drops dead.

[Pai's cover has been blown and Sheng Kuan has him cornered]
Pai Cheng-Tien, needn't run. You can't escape from me now!
Sheng Kuan Yuen... don't you believe that your Eagle Claw can beat everyone, it's not quite that invincible.

[chuckles wickedly]
Our two techniques... for many years have been rivals. But today though, we'll see the end of yours.
Hmmph! Well don't you be too sure! I'm not scared of you! I'm ready to fight you, right now!
Good! But it's gonna be your last fight for sure!
[gets into the Eagle Claw stance and prepares for combat]

[after Chien Fu surprises him with his new technique]
That technique! That isn't Snake Fist style! What is that?
